- ✅ `GetExitCodeForError()` maps categories to exit codes
- ✅ `ErrorCategoryNotFound` added to enum
- ✅ `CategorizeError()` detects not-found errors using `IsNotFound()` methods
- Requirement 3: Panic recovery - ✅ Panic recovery added in main.go
- Requirement 4: E2E tests - ❌ Tests failing

- Requirement: Debug mode - Not verified in tests

